===Etymology===
From Late {{inh|en|enm}}, borrowed from {{bor|en|frm|vocatif}}, from {{der|en|la|vocātīvus||for calling}}; a calque of Ancient Greek {{m|grc|κλητῐκή||for calling; vocative case}} &ndash; from {{m|la|voco|vocāre|to call}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro||*wokʷ-}}, [[o-grade]] of {{m|ine-pro|*wekʷ-|t=give vocal utterance, speak}}. See Latin {{m|la|vōx}}.

